  "remarks": "TAi.094 Title: a) Maulavi b) Mullah. Designation: Governor of Helmand Province under the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Supreme Council as of 2009. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Alokozai tribe. Member of Taliban leadership in Helmand Province, Afghanistan. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on3 Sep 2003, 18 Jul 2007, 21 Sep 2007 and 13 Feb 2012)",
